OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1783954167
OL,3,CTeen found dead in river was 'heart of
OL,4,Cour family'
OL,6,FA teenager who died after getting into
OL,7,Fdifficulty in a river has been
OL,8,Fdescribed as the "heart" of his family.
OL,10,FLeon Pafu Ngoy was pulled from the
OL,11,FRiver Irwell two days after he was
OL,12,Fseen entering the water at Clifton
OL,13,FCountry Park in Salford on Saturday 27
OL,14,FJune.
OL,16,FThe 15-year-old's family have
OL,17,Fdescribed him as a much-loved son,
OL,18,Fbrother, nephew, and friend.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
