PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1783954167
OL,3,CTeen found dead in river was 'heart of
OL,4,Cour family'
OL,6,FHis family said: "Leon was our baby,
OL,7,Four brother, our best friend and the
OL,8,Fheart of our family. He was kind,
OL,9,Frespectful, thoughtful and loved by
OL,10,Feveryone who knew him.
OL,12,F"No matter where he went, Leon brought
OL,13,Fenergy, laughter and happiness. People
OL,14,Fwill always remember his infectious
OL,15,Fsmile, his sense of humour and the way
OL,16,Fhe treated others with kindness and
OL,17,Fcompassion.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
