OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1783954167
OL,3,CTeen found dead in river was 'heart of
OL,4,Cour family'
OL,6,F"Leon had just completed his GCSEs and
OL,7,Fwas excited about the future. He loved
OL,8,Fbasketball, fashion, music and
OL,9,Fspending time with family and friends.
OL,10,FHe had big ambitions and dreams he was
OL,11,Flooking forward to pursuing."
OL,13,FLeon's family described his death as a
OL,14,F"tragic accident" and called on others
OL,15,Fto not enter the water in warm weather.
OL,17,FThey said: "If Leon could speak to
OL,18,Fothers today, we believe he would have
OL,19,Fone important message: no matter how
OL,20,Fsafe the water may look, it is never
OL,21,Fworth taking the risk.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1783954167
OL,3,CTeen found dead in river was 'heart of
OL,4,Cour family'
OL,6,F"We will always wonder what might have
OL,7,Fbeen if different choices had been
OL,8,Fmade. If Leon had gone to the local
OL,9,Fswimming baths instead of the Clifton
OL,10,FCountry Park that day, he would still
OL,11,Fbe with us.
OL,13,F"In sharing Leon's story, we hope that
OL,14,Fother families never have to
OL,15,Fexperience the unimaginable pain and
OL,16,Fheartbreak that we are living through.
OL,17,FLeon was deeply loved, and we will
OL,18,Fcarry his memory with us always."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
