PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1783954167
OL,3,CTeen found dead in river was 'heart of
OL,4,Cour family'
OL,6,FSpeaking shortly after Leon's body was
OL,7,Ffound, Detective Inspective Dave Ogden
OL,8,Fsaid his death was "an incredibly
OL,9,Fupsetting reminder of the serious
OL,10,Frisks associated with open water".
OL,12,FHe said: "We understand people want to
OL,13,Fmake the most of the warm weather, but
OL,14,Fwe would urge everyone to stay safe
OL,15,Fand avoid entering reservoirs, rivers,
OL,16,Fcanals or ponds. Please take care and
OL,17,Fenjoy the weather in a safe way."
OL,26,@yD@aO]
